 開始已經係必蝕架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你曾經有過一刻係賺咩？"},{"pid":"9d41b0fe7bf78de082ca9cf67701dbe21771f953","tid":1362823,"uid":167879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6d27fbc695a6ba0d46c7ed39c4d43e7d88c61833","tid":1362823,"uid":64603,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"dd4713ba7a847c770eb00b9c02f4e6fa6f3e5eec","tid":1362823,"uid":32995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"97dafeab5742aee6a05dc115cb0aa5356dfff369","tid":1362823,"uid":23672,"like":44,"dislike":1,"score":43,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T03:41:01.000Z","msg":"揸車不嬲點計都唔會用「抵」字黎形容啦<br />\n 日日坐的士出入都平過養車"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T03:51:27.000Z","msg":"的確係....一計就覺得係完全唔抵玩<br />\n岩岩成家立室, 所以先諗下點整理下D支出"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T04:15:08.000Z","msg":"既然成家立室，咁有小朋友未？ <br />\n<br />\n如果打算生小朋友，頭幾年有車的確好幫到手，車太太做檢查，車自己同太太父母睇或湊BB，車BB出街連同一大堆用品.....直到返幼稚園前架車都好有用。 <br />\n<br />\n如果無打算生小朋友，除非特別鍾意駕駛感覺，否則無閒錢養車的話就坐的士好過。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T10:23:53.000Z","msg":"ex7ly"},{"pid":"f4fcc1553e309b8c0e4ccaae6c2def467f3ebcfa","tid":1362823,"uid":32995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1446ddeb9680f159d6211fc91122f23b1f8086e3","tid":1362823,"uid":230043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:58:34.000Z","msg":"要計住計住嘅快手賣左佢啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港地如果唔係為搵食嘅,  &quot;車&quot; 只係用黎玩, 係興趣黎, 係燒銀紙嘅. 同你玩 hi-fi, 相機 1樣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申: 屋企有車都懶揸, 出入call 的士 uber 好過"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T11:48:29.000Z","msg":"其實架車原本係諗住同屋企人SHARE用, <br />\n點知買左之後佢地完全冇人揸過, 變左得我自己一個揸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad